---

This file contains the setup steps necessary to get the CD backups module
working under Debian with MySQL. It also assumes that the MySQL database
name is "freemed".

* Add "www-data" to the cdrecording group in /etc/group.
* Add "www-data" to the mysql group in /etc/group.
* Execute "chmod g+rx /var/lib/mysql/freemed".
* Execute "chmod u+s  /usr/bin/cdrecord /usr/bin/mkisofs"

